.content
  [名前]
  %p
    = product.name
  [価格]
  %p 
    = product.price
  [商品説明]
  %p 
    = product.explanation
  [商品状態]
  %p
    = product.condition
  [発送までの日数]
  %p
    = product.preparationdays
  [発送費負担]
  %p
    = product.is_shipping_buyer
  [ブランド]
  %p
    = product.brand
  [カテゴリー番号]
  %p
    = product.category_id
  [画像]
  %p
  - product.pictures.each do |picture|
    = image_tag picture.image.url